snippet.title: Double Kick Heroes - Early Access Reveal
snippet.description:
Unleash hellish METAL on zombies!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/589670/Double_Kick_Heroes/?utm_source=yt

----------------------
Bored with bland fake violin soundtracks ? Double Kick Heroes is a mashup of a shoot'em up with a frenetic rhythm game backed by an awesome METAL tune!

Website : http://doublekickheroes.rocks/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/headbang_club
Presskit : http://press.doublekickheroes.com/sheet.php?p=double_kick_heroes
